===========================================================================

Documentation is in
~/bin/src/findbugs/doc/index.html

Error messages are better explained at
~/bin/src/findbugs/doc
~/bin/src/findbugs/doc/bugDescriptions.html

===========================================================================

Example usage:

(Avoid my laptop, or use the -conserveSpace argument (and not -maxHeap
argument).)

cd $inv
make daikon.jar

cd $inv/java
~/tmp/findbugs-0.7.4/bin/findbugs -emacs -textui -maxHeap 750 -outputFile findbugs-output $inv/daikon.jar

For xml output, use:
  -xml -outputFile out.xml

===========================================================================

Bugs to report:

----------------

Also see ~/java/FindbugsTest.java
Run this command:
cd ~/java
javac FindbugsTest.java
findbugs -textui -emacs FindbugsTest*.class

